     <div style="width: 90%;  position: absolute; top: 20px; text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:200%;">107.1</p><p style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:20px;">Beheren van gebruikers en groepen</p></div>

<div style="position: absolute; top: 150px; left:400px; text-align:left; font-size:100%;">

<ul>
<li style="list-style:disc;">/etc/passwd</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">/etc/shadow</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">/etc/skel</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">useradd</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">passwd</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">usermod</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">chage</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">userdel</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">/etc/group</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">groupadd</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">groupmod</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">groupdel</li>
</ul>

</div>

	<div id="container" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; font-size:40%;">
  		<div id="left"><a href="http://www.linuxamsterdam.nl" target="_blank"><img src="la.svg" width=204px height=68px></a></div>
  		<div id="right"><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" target="_blank"><img src="cc_by-sa.svg" width=88px height=31px></a></div>
