<!-- _etc_passwd-intro-00 -->
    <div id="_etc_passwd-intro-00" style="position: absolute; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translate3d(1000px, -1500px, 0px) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) scale(1); transform-style: preserve-3d; "  class="step slide past" data-x="1000" data-y="-1500">

     <div style="width: 90%;  position: absolute; top: 20px; text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:200%;">/etc/passwd</p><p style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:20px;"> </p></div>

<div style="position: absolute; top: 200px; left:100px; right:100px; text-align:left; font-size:100%;">

<ul>
<li style="list-style:disc;">De gebruikers staan in de file '/etc/passwd'</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Het password echter staat er niet (meer) in</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Iedereen kan deze file inzien.</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Een 'x' als paswoord geeft aan dat deze staat in '/etc/shadow'</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Elke gebruiker heeft een unieke User ID.</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Lage user ID's zijn voor systeem accounts</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Hoge user ID's zijn meestal voor gebruikers</li>
</ul>
</div>

	<div id="container" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; font-size:40%;">
  		<div id="left"><a href="http://www.linuxamsterdam.nl" target="_blank"><img src="la.svg" width=204px height=68px></a></div>
  		<div id="right"><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" target="_blank"><img src="cc_by-sa.svg" width=88px height=31px></a></div>
  		<div id="center">LPIC-1 | Section 107.1 | Page 3/39</div>  

	</div>
</div>
<!-- _etc_passwd-intro-01 -->
    <div id="_etc_passwd-intro-01" style="position: absolute; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translate3d(2000px, -1500px, 0px) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) scale(1); transform-style: preserve-3d; "  class="step slide past" data-x="2000" data-y="-1500">

     <div style="width: 90%;  position: absolute; top: 20px; text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:200%;">/etc/passwd</p><p style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:20px;"> </p></div>

<div style="position: absolute; top: 200px; left:100px; right:100px; text-align:left; font-size:100%;">

<ul>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Het formaat in /etc/passwd file is als volgt:</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">username:password:uid:gid:comment:homedir:shell</li>
<br>
<li style="list-style:disc;">username is de gebruikersnaam bv. 'dion'</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">password is bv. 'x' (staat dus in '/etc/shadow')</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">uid is de User ID bv. '1000'</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">gid is de Group ID bv. '1000'</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">comment is het commentaar bv 'Dion Dresschers'</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">homedir bv. '/home/dion'</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">shell bv. '/bin/bash'</li>

</ul>
</div>

	<div id="container" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; font-size:40%;">
  		<div id="left"><a href="http://www.linuxamsterdam.nl" target="_blank"><img src="la.svg" width=204px height=68px></a></div>
  		<div id="right"><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" target="_blank"><img src="cc_by-sa.svg" width=88px height=31px></a></div>
  		<div id="center">LPIC-1 | Section 107.1 | Page 4/39</div>  

	</div>
</div>

