<!-- _etc_shadow-intro-00 -->
    <div id="_etc_shadow-intro-00" style="position: absolute; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translate3d(5000px, -1500px, 0px) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) scale(1); transform-style: preserve-3d; "  class="step slide past" data-x="5000" data-y="-1500">

     <div style="width: 90%;  position: absolute; top: 20px; text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:200%;">/etc/shadow</p><p style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:20px;"> </p></div>

<div style="position: absolute; top: 150px; left:100px; right:100px; text-align:left; font-size:100%;">

<ul>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Vroeger stonden de paswoorden in de '/etc/passwd'</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Nu staan ze in de file '/etc/shadow' die alleen 'root' kan lezen</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Het formaat in de '/etc/passwd' file is:</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">username:pwd:timesincechange:minpwdlifetime...</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">...:maxpwdlifetime:warningdays:inactivedays...</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">...:daysaccountdisabled:expiredate</li>

<li style="list-style:disc;">Handiger is 'chage -l <i>gebruiker</i>'</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Een '*' als paswoord betekent dat deze inactief is</li>
</ul>
</div>

	<div id="container" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; font-size:40%;">
  		<div id="left"><a href="http://www.linuxamsterdam.nl" target="_blank"><img src="la.svg" width=204px height=68px></a></div>
  		<div id="right"><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" target="_blank"><img src="cc_by-sa.svg" width=88px height=31px></a></div>
  		<div id="center">LPIC-1 | Section 107.1 | Page 7/39</div>  

	</div>
</div>
